                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-65-off391 t18000219-65-cd392"></join>, a shirt, value 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000219-65-victim590" type="victimName">
